<headline>Winter Weather Advisory issued January 20 at 11:49AM EST until January 20 at 6:00PM EST by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 PM EST /5 PM
CST/ THIS EVENING...
* WHAT...Lake effect snow. Additional snow accumulations of up
to one inch.
* WHERE...In Indiana, La Porte County. In Michigan, Berrien
County.
* WHEN...Until 6 PM EST /5 PM CST/ this evening.
* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. The hazardous
conditions could impact the evening commute.</description>
<instruction>Slow down and use caution while traveling.</instruction>
